{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/editing-lightworks-import-playback-cue-points/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Now that you know <a href=\"/setting-up-your-first-lightworks-project/\" title=\"Setting Up Your First Lightworks Project\">how to set up a project in Lightworks</a>, I’m sure you are dying to edit something, so lets jump right into this. Throughout this tutorial, I’m going to be editing the “<a href=\"https://www.thehelloworldprogram.com/linux/path-adventure/\">Path to Adventure</a>” episode. Follow along by downloading the assets linked below (right click the link and choose save as).</p>\n<p><a href=\"/6d9334873cb462cfe57620363ac94bf2/path_to_adventure_video.tar.gz\">Path To Adventure Video Assets</a>.</p>\n<p>Create a new 30 fps project and import the three video files. I’ve already converted them to a Lightworks preferred format, so despite what I’ve said before, you can import them with the “Copy Local” or “Create Link” option instead of transcoding them. Create a bin for your footage, a bin for you edits, and a rack for your bins. Then import the footage and drop it in your footage bin. You do remember <a href=\"/setting-up-your-first-lightworks-project/\" title=\"Setting Up Your First Lightworks Project\">how to do all of that</a>, right?</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 678px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.50000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'230\\'%20viewBox=\\'0%200%20400%20230\\'%20preserveAspectRatio=\\'none\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M5%208L4%20119v111h225v-17l-1-111V7H117L5%208m289%200h-64v66h72l75%201h2V8h-85M16%2059v27h94V34h-6l-47-1H16v26m61-20c0%203%200%203-3%203-2%200-3-1-3-2h-1c0%202-4%202-4%201l-2-1v2l-3-1h-1l-1%201v12c1%202%2019%202%2021%200%202-1%202-8%200-11l-2-5-1-2v3m169%200c0%203%200%203%202%202%201-2%201-2%202-1l6%201%2013%201c-1%201%200%201%201%201l2-2h6c1-4%200-4-17-4h-11l-2-1c-2%200-2%201-2%203M52%2062l-4%202v9h7c6%200%207-1%207-3s-1-2-5-2l-6-2c-2-1-2-2%209-2l13-2H52m-36%2055c0%2022%200%2024%202%2025l2%201c1%201%202-2%203-5l2-5v-1c0-1%200-2%201-1l2%201c5%200%205%200%203%201s-4%2011-3%2012a582%20582%200%200035-2c-4-4-5-8-3-9s8%204%207%206c-1%201%201%202%204%201l3-4v2c0%206%202%207%2015%207h9v-4a1599%201599%200%20002%202l5%201h5V92H63l-47%201v24m4%2034l4%201h-8v52h21l22%201a110%20110%200%200027%200l13%201h14l-13-1-13-1h23v-16c0-21%200-20%202-21l-1-2v-14a1280%201280%200%2000-91%200m43%207l1%201-2%202c-7%203-6%205%204%208%2011%204%2010%205-4%202l-13-3h-3l3%203%204%204h23l-17%204-6%202%201%201c5%200%2011%207%209%2010l1%202h12c6-2%206-2%207%200s1%202%202-2c1-11-2-21-10-29l-4-5h-1c0%202-4%203-4%201l-1-1h-2\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Lightworks bins and racks\"\n        title=\"Lightworks bins and racks\"\n        src=\"/static/884483ae0ab06aa772424bd9c63248f3/e8ec2/Selection_001.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/884483ae0ab06aa772424bd9c63248f3/f06cd/Selection_001.jpg 240w,\n/static/884483ae0ab06aa772424bd9c63248f3/a5e48/Selection_001.jpg 480w,\n/static/884483ae0ab06aa772424bd9c63248f3/e8ec2/Selection_001.jpg 678w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 678px) 100vw, 678px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>By default, Lightworks shows all of your bin contents as thumbnails. You may like this setup, but I find it a little cluttered. You can change this to a list view by clicking on the bin view icon at the top of your bin and selecting “list”.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 50%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'199\\'%20viewBox=\\'0%200%20400%20199\\'%20preserveAspectRatio=\\'none\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M392%2011l-37%201-38%201v88l61%203h22V10h-4l-4%201M12%2024l-1%2087v88h293v-17l-1-88V23H158L12%2024m8%2010l1%203%201-1c0-2%203-2%204%200l4%201h5l3-2%201-2v2l2%203v-2l1-3v-2h-3c-1%202-2%202-2%201h-8l-3%201-1%201v-3l-2-1c-3%200-3%200-3%204m198%201v4h14v-9h-14v5m-37%2024l2%203%202%203-19%201c-15%200-18%200-19%202-1%203%201%204%2020%203%2019%200%2019%200%2016%204l-1%203%2024-10-4-2a277%20277%200%2001-21-7M20%2079a679%20679%200%20013%2049l3%201h3l-3%201c-2%202-1%202%2010%202%2013%201%2093%200%2094-1l1-31V70H20v9m50%206v8c0%203%205%204%209%203l7-1c10%202%2015-5%2010-13-1-2-2-2-14-2H69l1%205m-7%2019l-7%202%201%205%201%205h6c6%201%2012%200%2011-2v-3c1-1%200-1-3-1-6%200-12-2-12-3l11-1c11%200%2018-1%2016-2l2-1h4c1-2-24-1-30%201m-42%2031a462%20462%200%20002%2048c1%202%205%201%207-2%201-3%204-3%206-2l3%201v1l-1%203v3l-1%204c-2%200-2%201%201%203%202%202%203%202%2017%202h14l-1-5c0-4%200-5%201-3s3%204%203%202l-1-3-2-5c0-2%200-2%204%200%202%200%204%202%205%203%202%202%206%205%208%205l3-7c1-4%202-7%203-6l-1%207c-4%2010-2%2013%2011%2013%2015%200%2016-1%2012-12l-1-6c1%200%204%207%204%2010%201%203%202%203%205%203h5c4%201%204-2%204-31v-27H76l-55%201m35%2011v5c0%203%201%204%206%204%206%201%2010%201%2010-1l-3-1-2-1c0-2%200-3%202-3%205%200%203-2-2-2a304%20304%200%2001-11-1m37%207h-1c-1-2-3%204-2%206s3%203%202%200l1-1h7c7-2%207-2%206%200-1%203-9%207-9%205%200-3-3-1-3%203v3l1-1%203-1c3%201%209-1%209-3l1-2v-9h-6c-4-2-8-2-9%200\\'%20fill=\\'%23d3d3d3\\'%20fill-rule=\\'evenodd\\'/%3e%3c/svg%3e'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"Set bin to list view\"\n        title=\"Set bin to list view\"\n        src=\"/static/538636f7fa9c7bb87151c4e907e8c82d/10bbb/Selection_002.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/538636f7fa9c7bb87151c4e907e8c82d/f06cd/Selection_002.jpg 240w,\n/static/538636f7fa9c7bb87151c4e907e8c82d/a5e48/Selection_002.jpg 480w,\n/static/538636f7fa9c7bb87151c4e907e8c82d/10bbb/Selection_002.jpg 500w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Additionally, you can change the size of the thumbnails by clicking on the settings icon in the top right corner of your bin, and changing the “Thumb Size” drop-down to “Small”.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 624px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.416666666666664%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3csvg%20xmlns=\\'http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\\'%20width=\\'400\\'%20height=\\'181\\'%20viewBox=\\'0%200%20400%20181\\'%20preserveAspectRatio=\\'none\\'%3e%3cpath%20d=\\'M377%205a1118%201118%200%2001-99%203h-20v19h-10l-1-5v-5H143L15%2018h-3v163h209v-2c0-2%201-3%203-3v1c-3%201-2%204%200%204l2-1c0-3%202-3%204-2h1c0-2%203-1%204%201%200%202%200%202%201%201l1-1h2l2%202%202-2v-2l1%202%201%202%201-2h1c0%201%200%202%201%201v-3l2%202c0%202%202%203%204%201v-3l2%201h1c2-2%204-1%204%201v3l1-3%202-2v2c0%202%200%202%201%201l3-3v2l1%202%201-2c0-2%200-3%202-2v4l1-2h1c1%202%201%202%201%200l2-2%201%201%201%201%201-1%201-1v2c0%202%200%202%202%202s3%200%203-2c-1-2%203-3%204%200l1%203v-3l1-2v2l1%202%201-2h1c0%201%200%202%201%201v-